Description: 
  The * MungeSumstatsModified * package is a modified package for * MungeSumstatsModified *. This update introduces a local chain option to the 'leftover' function, eliminating the need to download the chain file repeatedly. No other modifications have been made.

URL: https://github.com/neurogenomics/MungeSumstats
BugReports: https://github.com/neurogenomics/MungeSumstats/issues
